Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐這邊的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 小遊鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩今天也很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小遊鳥動不動就摸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種島真好 能被小鳥遊稱讚可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 山田也這麼覺得？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田也想被人寵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我「好可愛 好可愛 不用工作也行哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 總覺得你想錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把山田撿來瓦古納利亞的音尾先生離去的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田難道不也又小又可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你寵我一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小鳥遊用鼻子哼著嘲笑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0}{\pos(617,300)\1c&H11AEEA&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\fad(700,700)}第2章
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0}{\pos(615,340)\1c&H11AEEA&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\fad(700,700)}「理想的家庭計劃」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只讓他像對種島那樣 對我好點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…好像不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬 請安慰一下你的妹妹山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我沒妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 山田根本不了解我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就讓我了解一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於哥哥候補的相馬 山田什麼都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬 你幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打工的時候 都做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 為什麼不告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡山田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這問題就回答了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別偷懶了 幹活去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任性和你的工作 到底哪個更重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我好頭疼相馬呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密主義者一個 有關自己的事啥都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想更了解相馬同盟 成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…咦 我也是成員？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 鯛魚燒真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜歡甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的名字聽起來很甜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.60,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：「佐藤」和「砂糖」的發音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 我要跟蹤相馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是悄悄跟在別人後面不太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種麻煩事 如果不是喜歡對方誰願意做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤是愛情的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛情？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教種島一些怪東西的話 小鳥遊會生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬 這其實是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤我？真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃點甜食 大腦能轉得快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 這下就能好好跟蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是早露餡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算跟蹤早露餡了 沒人會想到我就藏在男更衣室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 這種事果然不太好 出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 正是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰打電話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西就拿到老地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這時候了就別害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把錢拿來就會沒命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家人的命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什什什什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 他忘拿手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 不可以偷看別人的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只 只是看通話記錄而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報時台？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 相馬他是個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話給報時台 獨自玩懸疑遊戲的可憐智障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的相馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的相馬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可憐的相馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是的 只是作弄你們一下 玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一副遺憾的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 跟蹤結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過後果概不負責哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬先生好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也是開玩笑的 開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟小鳥遊覺得可愛的種島不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的男性恐怖症要是治好了 他就不會理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 乾脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持這樣也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去幹活 伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遊鳥 你幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你們說 小伊波那麼喜歡小遊鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他一點都沒察覺 小伊波好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 小鳥遊真遲鈍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼察覺不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我想給她打打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:08:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種島 這種事即使第三者介入 也成不了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤先生 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得佐藤先生的話 好有份量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我去讓小遊鳥注意到小伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遊鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊波她很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩比她更小更可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不認輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得小伊波最近有點不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著小遊鳥就會臉紅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時扭扭捏捏的啦 一鼓作氣就揍上來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 她以前就是這樣的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那小遊鳥喜歡什麼類型的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了又小又可愛的以外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為異性的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會施暴力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 想治好小伊波的男性恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得小遊鳥應該更接近她一點…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 多稱讚下小伊波可愛之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一副不願意的表情！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個當成是小伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子名叫伊波哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波 你好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不錯 聲音再大點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波 你真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個啦 這個！這叫伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是 我剛才沒看到娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰都嚇軟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:10:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 種島為了我這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在保持這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣也挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還沒習慣 就被男的那麼表揚的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我怕會受不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波 量很大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是出於好意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻讓你的腰和心靈都產生了負擔 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種島 你好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小遊鳥傳染了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 還是沒能了解到相馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:11:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然會好好寵山田的 只有音尾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易被人騙 別人說什麼都樂呵呵地傾聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長拒絕別人 超級爛好人的音尾先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生 音尾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想回應她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我死也不放開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白藤 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是土特產
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你是音尾啊 看到零食前沒記起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你為了尋找行蹤不明的妻子而到處旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開的時間也該有個底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為就算我不在也沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有問題 人家會擔心吧

Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土產 時間長了味道會變差的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是這方面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生 又想用食物勾引杏子姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拿回來的話 白藤會發怒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且根本想不起我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 山田還不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上離開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果現在把音尾先生給砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏子姐就沒法獲得禮物了 好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大叔便當了 店長就沒空吃聖代了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 大叔連店長的那份工作也一起做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來轟很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到職場的流血事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得這麼恐怖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼沒法用這點機智讓轟喜歡上你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤先生 相馬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生回來小葵很開心 實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這有點唐突 人類啊 頭上其實是死角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死角?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不論發生什麼事都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 可以隨意擺弄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全的拿別人當出氣筒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遊鳥 佐藤他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又欺負你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就覺得了 佐藤綁頭髮技術很差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點不是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近特別愛欺負人啊 佐藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生氣了 以牙還牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以牙還牙?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向佐藤先生復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣的我是很恐怖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇應該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要問別人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 做些惹人厭惡的事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹人厭惡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如 無視他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把東西藏起來 在鞋子裡面放圖畫釘 打無聲電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遊鳥 極惡之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問相馬先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 感覺真問對人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓佐藤感到不快？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他做你討厭的事不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對相馬來說 程度很輕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實說「自己戀愛不順 也別拿人家當出氣筒」比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那前輩的性命就有危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 種島 髮型復原了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 頸子會酸 不跟你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為佐藤先生個子大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那還真對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:16:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的頸子也很酸 因為種島太矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 迅速遭到了反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹想想總被人說矮的人的感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒被人說過矮 因為比我高的人不多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遊鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦 佐藤君 太孩子氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼 種島
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時老被欺負 所以說想復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你生氣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒生氣 竟然被小不點說成是小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是在生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老欺負我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 僅次於身材矮小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱能使人變大哦 這不蠻好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變大…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 今後也同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什麼情況 今後我依然要被欺負嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:34.57,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 呐 佐藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼下去 佐藤和前輩的關係會逐漸變壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 馬上就會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤先生給了我零食！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田也去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田不小心忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我要去確認下備用品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田原來是這樣的性格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你以前要更懂事點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 山田之前偽裝得很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 最近很迷數碼相機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點找到你夫人就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這個節骨眼兒上說這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵她很開心呢 讓她多撒撒嬌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟帶她來這裡的恩人回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直在等音尾先生歸來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你收我做養女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養女?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生是山田理想中的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用自己再生 很省事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫁人 吸乾父母的養老金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 養子不是那麼容易就能當的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說 該好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生 不好好訓她 會得寸進尺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從剛才起就在生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這氣勢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說 當班中就該去幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 音尾先生對山田來說 就像是前輩對我來說一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用工作的這份喜悅我也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊波 小葵說音尾先生是她理想中的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生很溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊波以後會成為一個好母親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想中的爸爸跟媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想中的家庭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想中的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田超幸福 跟理想中的爸爸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份幸福能永遠保持就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾 會逗留一陣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 兩三天內會離開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田 不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把山田…丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 帶禮物給你 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當做養子收養我的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 不過我最近記性不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請記下來 記下來很重要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:29.27,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生暫時又不會回來了

Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候能治癒山田的果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有女人的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千代~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種島~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼了

Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監督 我跑不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改寫記錄什麼的根本沒希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為山田精神萎靡嘛

